Basic Design Principles:
1. colors
2. typography

- Color Theory = color wheel, meaning of colors, color combinations
- subtle color combination - monochromatic = mtlb eik hi color choose krke uske shades yani eik lighter effect aur eik aur lighter effect us color
- impactful color combination - complementary = ye attractive combinations dikhaane ke liye use hota hai jo impact daalay aur ye colors color wheel main opposite hote hain
- high contrast combination - triadic = color wheel main equally seperated 3 colors hote hain ye triadic form main
- detail main prhne ke liye = canva color wheel

- Typography = style & appearance of text, font families (sans-seif, serif, monospace cursive, fantasy), 
- professional font style = times new roman, calibiri, roboto, 
- fun or funky = fantasy fonts
- one section = maximum 2 fonts unless and until koi graphical chz nhi banaa rahe

Icons = font awesome, google fonts